Package de.fha.dpmi.versioning

Version Graph implementation by a Version Control System

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    VersionGraph
    a version graph for model versioning; it consists of branches which contain versions
    VersionGraphController
    Controls the creation, removal, loading and storing of version graphs
    VersionGraphDVCS
    Represents a version graph implemented in a distributed versioning control system
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Branch
    Represents a branch of the version graph
    UniqueOrderedVersion
    Stores versions and computes a total order of given versions
    Version
    Represents on version on the version graph
    VersionGraphControllerImpl
    implements the version graph controller
    VersionGraphDVCSBase
    implementation base class for DVCS
    VersionGraphDVCSGit
    Implements a version graph using the Git DVCS
    VersionGraphFileIO
    file input/output for files containing version graph information, e.g.
    VersionGraphImpl
    Implementation of a version graph providing general methods for creation, removal and storage
    VersionsSortedListTotalOrdering
    Stores the total order of versions on a version graph
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    VersionGraphCredentialException
    exception thrown during version graph handling
    VersionGraphException
    Exception thrown during version control operations
    VersionGraphFileIOException
    exception thrown during reading/writing version graphs from/to disk
